// All factorizations are clipped to dimensions â‰¤ 7 (the player-facing
// dimension cap) and verified byte-for-byte against the symmetrized
// matmul tensor at encode time (see scripts/extract_alphatensor.py).
//
// Each board is encoded as a flat string of length RÂ·rowsÂ·cols
// using the single-character-per-cell legend
//   "_" = âˆ’2   "-" = âˆ’1   "." = 0   "+" = +1   "=" = +2
// pages laid out one after another, each page in row-major. Any
// preset whose `alphabet` field is absent uses the default
